data.description: The perfect home in the country is waiting for you at 29630 Kloecker Road, just outside of Hempstead, in the highly popular area of northern Waller County. Set on a 1.9-acre tract, this contemporary home offers all the modern conveniences with plenty of outside space for you and your animals to enjoy. Light restrictions are in place to protect your investment value. The 2,049-sf home features two open porches, attached garage and a separate 624-sf workshop/storage building with concrete floor and electricity. Other exterior features include a sprinkler system, aerobic septic system, and Leaf Guard gutters. The interior split-floor plan includes three large bedrooms, 2 baths, office, living room, kitchen, breakfast area, and utility room. While outside the congestion of the big city, it offers easily accessible connections to the metropolitan areas of Bryan-College Station, Houston, The Woodlands, and Austin via SH 6, US 290, and FM 1488.
